Uses of Package
org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.callbacks

  • Packages that use org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.callbacks 
    Package Description
    org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation
    Contains all classes to activate the AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin (AKA chartjs-plugin-annotation.js ) for CHART.js.
  • Classes in org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation.callbacks used by org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation 
    Class Description
    AdjustScaleRangeCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set adjustScaleRange property at runtime, to AbstractAnnotation.
    CalloutPositionCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set position property at runtime, to Callout.
    DrawTimeCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set drawTime property at runtime, in all annotations.
    FillCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set fill property at runtime, to Arrow.
    LabelAlignPositionCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set position property at runtime, to BoxLabel.
    LabelPositionCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set position property at runtime, to LineLabel.
    LengthCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set length property at runtime, to Arrow.
    MarginCallback
    Callback interface to set margin property at runtime in Callout item.
    SideCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set side property at runtime, to Callout.
    SidesCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set sides property at runtime, to PolygonAnnotation.
    StartCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set start property at runtime, to Callout.
    ValueCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set:
    xMin for BoxAnnotation, EllipseAnnotation and LineAnnotation xMax for BoxAnnotation, EllipseAnnotation and LineAnnotation yMin for BoxAnnotation, EllipseAnnotation and LineAnnotation yMax for BoxAnnotation, EllipseAnnotation and LineAnnotation xValue for PointAnnotation yValue for PointAnnotation value for LineAnnotation, infinitive line endValue for LineAnnotation, infinitive line
    properties at runtime.
    ZCallback
    Callback interface of AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin to set z property at runtime.
